{
  "title": "wakapakapalra",
  "titleCh": "赤腳仙子",
  "soundPath": null,
  "sentence": [
    {
      "chinese": "群山環繞的霧臺，向來有「長跑選手搖籃」之稱。在過去對外道路不通的時代，部落族人要下山到平地（水門），得走上八到十個小時；到自家地耕作地，也得花上少則一、二個小時，多則三、四個小時，到哪兒都須仰賴雙腳。這樣的環境，孕育出族人強健的腳力，有過人的耐力、輕快的步伐。",
      "ab": "ikai ki kiangithalringulu ki lregelrege ka Vudai, nyuku ki tahalrabuwabuale kyaiya kisunagane. sa kadruwana ku kaelrelrea ku atangukakaiya papubabadhaa ku igayga, kai mapapangale luai mudrata muSwimungu, tahangwavalru lukai ngumangeale ki tuki dwadavace, lu twalai ki tauwana mumawma, lu adethe ainguea ngudrusa ki tuki, lu adaili ngwatulru ngusupate ki tuki, luuwa ki iniiniinunga sakathaa ku drapale ku sahakaiya apamuininu, lakuni kitualrau si ikai ku sapukuwa ku vagisi, ikai ku saniange ku sakiadiadili, kaliyapai lu dadavace.",
      "order": "1",
